OL,3,CMystery man who allegedly swum to
OL,4,CJersey from France finally deported
OL,6,FA man who was found on a Jersey beach
OL,7,Fquoting Shakespeare and claiming to be
OL,8,Fa British citizen has been deported -
OL,9,Ftwo years since he arrived in the
OL,10,Fisland.
OL,12,FThe man who calls himself 'David Henry
OL,13,FLaw' was found at Rozel Bay in
OL,14,FSeptember 2024.
OL,16,FHe claimed he had swum 13 hours from
OL,17,FFrance to reach Jersey, but was
OL,18,Fsentenced to 15 months in prison for
OL,19,Ftwo charges, including entering Jersey
OL,20,Fillegally.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
