PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779390672
OL,3,CMystery man who allegedly swum to
OL,4,CJersey from France finally deported
OL,6,FHowever, 'Mr Law' was left in 'legal
OL,7,Flimbo' after his prison sentence
OL,8,Fended, as there was no obvious legal
OL,9,Fpathway for deportation without a
OL,10,Fconfirmed identity.
OL,12,FNow, after a year and eight months,
OL,13,Fthe Jersey Customs and Immigration
OL,14,FService (JCIS) has announced that the
OL,15,Fman has finally been deported.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38203
