CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779390672
OL,3,CMystery man who allegedly swum to
OL,4,CJersey from France finally deported
OL,6,FIn a statement released this morning
OL,7,F(Wednesday 20 May), JCIS said that
OL,8,Fthey had identified Mr Law's real
OL,9,Fnationality following "detailed and
OL,10,Flengthy enquiries" with jurisdictions
OL,11,Fin Europe and beyond.
OL,13,FHowever, JCIS and other Jersey
OL,14,Fauthorities have refused to confirm or
OL,15,Fdeny David Law's true identity and his
OL,16,Fhome nation.
OL,18,FThis is despite a recent report in the
OL,19,FJersey Evening Post, identifying the
OL,20,Fgentleman as a Chinese national named
OL,21,FMr Wang.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779390672
OL,3,CMystery man who allegedly swum to
OL,4,CJersey from France finally deported
OL,6,FThe JCIS's statement reads: "JCIS have
OL,7,Fidentified the individual's true
OL,8,Fnationality and identity and can
OL,9,Fconfirm that he is not a British
OL,10,Fnational and therefore has no right to
OL,11,Freside in Jersey.
OL,13,F"The individual was flown to the UK
OL,14,Fwith officers from JCIS on Tuesday 19
OL,15,FMay where he was met by UK Border
OL,16,FForce officials before being returned
OL,17,Fto his home country.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,383,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F382A1779390672
OL,3,CMystery man who allegedly swum to
OL,4,CJersey from France finally deported
OL,6,F"In line with other deportation cases,
OL,7,FJCIS will not provide comment in
OL,8,Frespect of the identity of the
OL,9,Findividual.
OL,11,F"JCIS can confirm that the man
OL,12,Fclaiming to be Mr Law did not at any
OL,13,Ftime apply for asylum in Jersey."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/6
